Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死去死去死 去死去死去死去死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再把你們劣質的基因傳下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發情的淫獸們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死 去死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?呐 這是大金剛?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 女人真是沒腦子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?但是很像哦 你看嘴唇這麼厚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為這個理由的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠算學校的老爺爺也是大金剛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...可是啊 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:51.65,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(宿海仁太)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的野獸 相當的 兇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好狡猾 面碼也要吃 鹽拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:07.94,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(本間芽衣子)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼要吃蛋花 蛋花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 要變成荷包蛋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把雞蛋攪開 攪開 攪開啊  -噢 怎麼 吃拉麵?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:33.53,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 叔叔 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 仁太 也給我做一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:43.03,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給叔叔做就不給面碼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能別再看見什麼都說可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:47.25,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔也說面碼很可愛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?這可是個好詞哦 哪裡都能用上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞蛋要什麼樣的?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個荷包蛋 別煮成蛋花了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏心 偏心 偏心中年人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視 電視...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 貓咪可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸狀態很正常 這樣看來果然是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡椒 胡椒 胡椒 胡椒 好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筷子在哪 筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?怎麼了 在家裡中暑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可愛 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時侯的夏天...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還是仁太抓的最大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的我...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-呐 鶴見子  -怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.85,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}(給仁太君 我去上班了 你好好休息下)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我病了 確實是病了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定我一直承受的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一直籠罩著我的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏天的炎熱成了形...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連思春期的性衝動也一起來了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-就算是我的壓力具象化成你出現在這裡  -誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼到現在才出現...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:06:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...為什麼是以成長後的姿態出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你問我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 也許...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要實現願望吧 面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望?什麼願望?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道願望怎麼實現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...但是 我覺得就是來實現願望的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實到底是為什麼出現的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口水都飛出來了 真是的 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力場!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.13,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是無敵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 夏天的猛獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.13,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼無敵...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的壓力 我的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先把那所謂的願望想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 對了 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是必須要大家一起才能實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?大家是指...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等下 等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有人在叫門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去開怎麼行啊 好了不要鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-安 安城...  -是anaru啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.87,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(安城鳴子)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別激動...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別激動?我又沒激動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩怎麼這麼沉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru看不見面碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師讓我轉交給你的暑假作業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才給我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還什麼暑假 我說...已經只剩兩天了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不像宿海 可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 你隨便找個地方扔了不得了 這破玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那種白癡高中我也不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來不來無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...你也太沒骨氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ana...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不拜託anaru呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 幫我們實現願望 anaru~ 就這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫她anaru
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:49.79,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(anal日語發音為anaru)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城也好 鳴子也好 要叫就叫這兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 anaru就是anaru哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對大家很好 有好多遊戲和漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是那時候的anaru了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拜託那個臭娘們 她也不肯幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭娘們?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是蠢女人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 那傢伙已經不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我討厭說anaru壞話的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 再去找anaru一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拜託她吧 仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拜託安城讓她幫忙實現願望你就會明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是安城 一切都和那時候不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁太 還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子還有眼鏡?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 買東西去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 說起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的表情 啊 有拉麵裡的蔥哦 牙齒上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 anaru家不在這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便散步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 以前是bombom吧 已經改成WcDonald了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 但是面碼更喜歡炸肉餅...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一個學校的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有外星人出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有個用雙截棍的女的在學校和他打的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?那是什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 我只是被兩個大媽搞壞了心情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會在意我這種人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城不是也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人 怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然的啊 只是我的幻覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現願望...嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來 這一定也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對面碼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢 很危險的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 面碼她...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒...沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 鳴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你去小仁家了?  -敲門!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?我沒敲?有什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-對了...  -只是順路去了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這和媽媽有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦 本想讓你把豆包給他拿去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己拿去不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 思春期 思春期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟人的...是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去參加暑期講習了 畢竟是重點高中嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本該穿在我身上的...高中的制服...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.04,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪集和鶴子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:12.26,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(松雪集 鶴見知利子)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-走了!  -哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是說面碼...啊不 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼是什麼意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到現在還在說這種東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有在上學對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試沒考好 進了個垃圾高中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不去上學 總是喊著本間芽衣子的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腦子是不是長蛆了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集是白癡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一提到本間芽衣子就像換了個人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和他一樣吧 集雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個沒看頭的傢伙 只有長相還好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦瓜也夠好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太!等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下 你應該明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 變得最多的 其實就是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...呐...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的壓力源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:16:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起 只會想起些不愉快的和不愉快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人心煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁...太...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候 那時候的夏天...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是這樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 定下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是超和平busters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好帥!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,busters是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是指厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要保護和平!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:52.63,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的和平?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的都有 各種和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那 仁太是隊長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那一天...那一天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁太啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是喜歡面碼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就說實話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們超和平busters不許有事瞞著大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太說啊 快點說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.65,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊 說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰 誰會喜歡這種醜女...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為她會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為面碼是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?這麼早就回來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到媽媽那邊去一下 飯熱一下再吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:20.74,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(洗好手 熱一下再吃 爸爸)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那笑臉...讓我心裡很不是滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來覺得明天道個歉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個明天 卻永遠都不會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 門開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那關上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...長這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...有好多白頭髮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要總這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰君...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次吃咖喱都要給姐姐供一份 真是看著難受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是姐姐最喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了還吃什麼飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐有點缺根筋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許還不知道自己已經死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼...自己已經死了這點事 還是知道的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:19:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道 它自己倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:04.71,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了 快收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 又不是我碰倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有 可惡的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功地把和平bust掉的我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺地開始疏遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼喜歡蛋花 蛋花!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙會去的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要 那時的明天...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能向面碼道歉的明天 一直想要...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的壓力源
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我一定是為了向面碼道歉才造出了一個面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 這樣下去...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:16.51,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}(穿喪服的團地妻)\N(人妻熟女的危險遊戲)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太重口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 正是這種病態才浪漫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?這不是仁太嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:29.35,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(久川鐵道)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們在這裡刻上名字吧
